sequenceDiagram
    actor T as Teknisi
    participant B as Browser
    participant API as GET /api/bandwidth
    participant P as MikroTik Pool
    participant Cache as Cache (TTL 10s)
    participant MT as MikroTik RouterOS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    T->>B: Buka /bandwidth
    B->>API: GET /api/bandwidth
    API->>P: mikrotikQuery("/ppp/active/print")
    P->>Cache: lookup("/ppp/active/print")
    alt cache hit
        Cache-->>P: cached array
    else cache miss
        P->>MT: connect (singleton)
        P->>MT: /ppp/active/print
        MT-->>P: [ {name, address, uptime, ...} ]
        P->>Cache: set TTL=10s
    end
    P-->>API: active sessions
    API->>P: mikrotikQuery("/queue/simple/print")
    P-->>API: queues[]
    API->>DB: SELECT customers JOIN packages
    DB-->>API: customers[]
    API->>API: merge(active, queues, customers)
    API-->>B: { connections, online, offline, throughput }
    B-->>T: Render tabel + grafik realtime
    Note over B,API: Frontend polling tiap 30 detik
